{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fd9e380e0b","title":"加紧督促桂粤湘三省期巩固广东防务","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"25cc5949ae","index":0,"year":1950,"month":12,"day":29,"articleId":"fd9e380e0b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"205be4c0a7","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"fd9e380e0b","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"邓、谭、赵、苏，指邓子恢、谭政、赵尔陆、苏静，当时分别任中南军区第二政治委员、第三政治委员、参谋长和副参谋长。"},{"id":"097db5ee27","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"fd9e380e0b","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指台湾国民党军队可能在广东登陆进犯。"},{"id":"0081b76b61","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"fd9e380e0b","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"衡州，今湖南衡阳。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c5fe762601","type":"title","text":"加紧督促桂粤湘三省割罪巩固广东防务","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"fd9e380e0b"},{"id":"205be4c0a7","type":"paragraph","text":"邓、谭、赵、苏：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"fd9e380e0b"},{"id":"097db5ee27","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）十二月二十四日关于总结秋季期经验的报告收到阅悉，甚好甚感，已发华东、西南、西北三区参考。（二）对桂粤湘三省剩非仍望加紧督促，务于五月三十一日以前彻底完成剩能任务，使广西的一个军（是否四十五军适宜）及二十一兵团能于六月上句集中梧州地区待命调动入粤，应付可能发生的事变。湖南应准备以一个军至退于五月间最好能在三四月间集中郴州、衡州线上待命。总之广东有事须由四野负责独力应付，保证战胜可能入侵之台湾军，巩固广东防务，望按此方针筹划剩汇工作及兵力部署","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"fd9e380e0b"},{"id":"0081b76b61","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"fd9e380e0b"},{"id":"2bf264cea3","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月二十九日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"fd9e380e0b"}],"page":{"id":"777197fa59","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"fd9e380e0b","start":471,"end":471}}}},"__N_SSG":true}